      "text": [
        "تْ لَهُ أَنَا حَائِضٌ فَقَالَ لَهَا «أَ حَيْضُكِ فِي يَدِكِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.154 - The Messenger of Allah (sw) said to one of his wives:\n\"Hand me the khumrah (a small prayer mat).\"\nShe replied: \"I am menstruating\"\nHe (sw) said: 'Is your menstruation in your hand?'"
        ]
      }
